# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Committed: platform shells, shared icons, hub back pill, example flows.
#
# The four shells (Web / mWeb / iOS / Android) took significant design-accuracy
# work and match the CGDS Figma "CG TY25 Nav & Shell" frames.
#
# Example flows live in src/prototypes/examples/ (W-2 upload, Finish & File) so
# new teammates have end-to-end references of "what good looks like." Everything
# in that folder IS committed.
#
# Per-user flows: /prototype scaffolds into src/prototypes/local/ by default —
# everything under local/ is gitignored, so your experiments stay on your
# machine. If you want to share a flow with the team, move it from
# local/ into examples/ and register it in src/prototypes/registry.tsx.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Per-user prototype flows + registry additions — not committed by default.
# OVERRIDE: this prototype (DIWM FY27) is being shared via GitHub Pages, so
# the local files ARE committed for backup. If you fork this prototype and
# want the original team behavior, uncomment the two lines below.
# src/prototypes/local/
# src/prototypes/registry.local.tsx

